Math Problem series with solution.


Question link
https://www.codingninjas.com/studio/problems/count-digits_8416387

Solution:

int countDigits(int n){
	int count = 0;
	int temp = n;
	while(temp != 0) {
		int last_dig = temp % 10;
		temp = temp / 10;
		if(last_dig > 0 && n % last_dig == 0)
			count = count + 1;
	}
	return count;
}

